# Marketing & Web UI

## Before coding UI

1. Read `design-system/halisaha/MASTER.md` (especially **HalıSaha Brand Overrides**)
2. Check `design-system/halisaha/pages/[page].md` if it exists (overrides Master)
3. For new patterns, use `halisaha-ui` skill or `ui-ux-pro-max` with `--stack nextjs`

## Tokens & Tailwind

- Colors/fonts from `src/styles/tokens.css` and `@theme` in `globals.css`
- No scattered hex values in components when a token exists

## Interaction (web)

- `cursor-pointer` on all clickable elements
- Hover/focus transitions: 150–300ms; respect `prefers-reduced-motion`
- Visible focus rings for keyboard navigation
- Touch targets: min 44×44px on mobile CTAs

## Accessibility

- Body text contrast ≥ 4.5:1 on `--text` / `--muted` over dark backgrounds
- Turkish copy; `lang="tr"` on `<html>`
- SVG icons for nav/CTAs; decorative ⚽ badges OK on marketing hero only

## Responsive

Test at 375px, 768px, 1024px, 1440px. No horizontal scroll on mobile.

## Patterns to reuse

- `Button` from `@/components/ui/Button`
- `RevealOnScroll` for section entrances
- `.field-bg` for pitch grid backgrounds on hero/invite pages
